          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叩见万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "使臣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你宣召卜式，怎么了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "使臣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卜式已经召来，现在午门候旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣他上殿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "使臣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁有旨：卜式上殿！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（使臣下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卜式上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "布衣躬畜牧，今日上丹墀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣，河南小民卜式，叩见天颜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻尔输家财助边，真乃爱国之士。但不知尔可愿为官？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小臣出身畜牧，未习吏事，不愿为官。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你既不愿为官，想是你家有何冤仇，不妨奏与孤王，替你昭雪就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小臣素来好施，与人无争，并无什么冤仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知你捐输巨款，有何需求？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣并无什么需求。只因万岁征讨匈奴，依小臣看来，凡我大汉臣民，贤能者应"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "守边死节，厚富者应尽力输财。只要全国上下，有此决心，何愁匈奴不灭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言之有理。待孤晓谕天下，矜式万民。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小臣怎敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！尔既出身畜牧，就命尔在上林替孤牧羊。封尔为中郎，长享爵禄。下殿去"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叩谢万岁下龙廷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "去做上苑牧羊的人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卜式下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "拂龙袖王退班后宫来进，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘彻",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "但愿得灭匈奴早庆升平。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "使臣→刘彻",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "刘彻→使臣",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "使臣→卜式",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "卜式→刘彻",
          "turns": 7
        },
        {
