    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "父老丁",
        "父老丙",
        "父老乙",
        "父老甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（父老甲、父老乙、父老丙、父老丁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宁为太平犬，"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老乙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不作离乱民。"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿匈奴灭，"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早日享太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老乙、父老丙、父老丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那匈奴连年为患，河南地方屡遭兵灾，仓库空虚。前年我们这里卜式先生捐"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "资赈济，我们才得活命。如今边患未灭，像卜先生这样的好人，不知道到哪里"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你还不知道哪？他老人家赈济我们，花了不少钱哪！前三年北边吃紧的时候，"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他老人家上书给皇上，愿意拿他的一半家财，捐助国家，扩充军备，去打外国"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人。皇上早就把他老人家聘请去啦，由上林牧羊起，就有了很好的成绩，一直"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "升官，真是连升三级。如今唤做了齐王太傅，那儿的百姓谁不拥护他老人家？"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怎么一点不知道呢？真是老糊涂了不是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想我乡里不靖，生计困难。何不去到临淄，投奔卜太傅，一来谢谢他老人家再"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "造之恩；二来投效乡里，寻个进身之计。不知列位意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好极啦！反正咱们在家里待着，也没有好日子过，要是有机会的话，咱们也可"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "以上前线去杀敌人，岂不也是一个英雄，名垂千古吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲、父老丙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此甚好。我们就此一同前往，请哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "卜先生待我等恩德高厚，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（父老甲下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老乙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "千里迢迢把齐投。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（父老乙下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "誓扫狼烟平贼寇，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（父老丙下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "大刀砍尽敌人的头！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
