    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "卜式",
        "父老丁",
        "父老丙",
        "父老乙",
        "父老甲",
        "院子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（父老甲、父老乙、父老丙、父老丁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一日离家一日深，"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老乙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "好似孤雁宿寒林。"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "披星戴月来齐境，"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不觉来到太傅门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊列位，看前面已是太傅府，我们少时进见，不可鲁莽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那个自然。大家小心就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "门上哪位在？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "劳烦通禀太傅：就说河南乡人们求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少待一时。"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请家爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卜式上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "河南父老们求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快去请他们进来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子暗下。父老甲、父老乙、父老丙、父老丁同进见，同跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人们与太傅叩头！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！列位少礼，请坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太傅在此，哪有小人们的座位？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "远道而来，又是同乡父老，哪有不坐之理！"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等告坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今年秋收可好，乡里可靖？"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年成倒也不差。只是地方不甚平靖。乡人们都好，问候太傅金安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳他们！列位远道到此，必有所为？"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等身受厚恩，无以为报；何况匈奴未平，故乡不靖。我们一来是看望太傅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位哪里话来！下官前者输财助边，散钱施赈，无非是尽我爱护国家乡党之心，"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "劝列位休提起恩德二字，"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太傅金石之言，我等敢不遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊太傅！听了你这一番话，真不愧救国的名言！小人不才，也忍不住热血奔腾，"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好倒好，只是万岁旨意下来，暂时不欲我齐国出兵。列位有此热忱，下官十分"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国破家亡无限恨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "毁家纾难胜古人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿匈奴齐扫尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "父老丁",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全仗男儿爱国心！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卜式",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
